# ==============================================================================
# OpenClaw + Ollama: macOS pf Anchor Ruleset
# ==============================================================================
# Description: This ruleset enforces a strict loopback-only policy for local 
# LLM infrastructure. It acts as a defense-in-depth failsafe in case the 
# application-level host bindings (127.0.0.1) fail or are misconfigured.
# ==============================================================================

# Allow explicitly routed loopback traffic to OpenClaw (3000) and Ollama (11434)
pass in quick on lo0 proto tcp from 127.0.0.1 to 127.0.0.1 port { 3000, 11434 }
pass in quick on lo0 proto tcp from ::1 to ::1 port { 3000, 11434 }

# Block ALL other inbound TCP traffic to these service ports from any interface
block in quick proto tcp from any to any port { 3000, 11434 }
